◆劉開鈴。1997。〈淺談中國學生學習美國文學的問題。〉《英美文學﹝史﹞教學與課程規劃研討會論文集。》高雄：中山大學。47-66。
◆Liu, Kai-ling. 1990. "Yeats and Auden: Views on the Function of Poetry." Collected Essays of the Third National Conference of English and American Literature. Kaohsiung: National San Yat-sen University. 215-27.

 
